1
00:01:40,580 --> 00:01:44,200
[A Moment But Forever]

2
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:47,150
[Episode 26]

3
00:01:47,789 --> 00:01:50,640
I hope he can use this power wisely

4
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,840
and live out his life

5
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,350
under the protection of Goddess Wushuang

6
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:55,560
without wasting

7
00:01:56,130 --> 00:01:58,820
the opportunity we've given him.

8
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,710
Why is the sky suddenly so bright?

9
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:25,240
Ji Tanyin.

10
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:27,280
Are you going back?

11
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:29,710
You might be in danger.

12
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:31,520
I won't.

13
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:33,150
Do you have to get involved in his affairs?

14
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:36,850
Excuse me, is Miss Ji here?

15
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,150
That's me.

16
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,950
Someone asked me to deliver this letter to you.

17
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,400
Enjoy.

18
00:02:58,710 --> 00:02:59,680
Miss, welcome.

19
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,590
This way.

20
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:10,240
If you have something so important

21
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,800
that you must tell me,

22
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,150
now is the time to say it.

23
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,630
The noodles here

24
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,960
don't look that great.

25
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,630
How come you and the High Priest of the Youhu Clan

26
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:20,280
never get tired of eating them?

27
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,079
I have something important to attend to today.

28
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:23,310
If you have nothing to say,

29
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:24,400
I'll be going.

30
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,840
You're upset?

31
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:29,710
Could it be...

32
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:31,150
he's seen through you

33
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,710
and known you're up to no good?

34
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,750
What are you talking about?

35
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:36,360
It can't be. There are plenty of women

36
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,560
skilled in craftsmanship in this world.

37
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,560
Besides me,

38
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,400
who else could have found out

39
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,030
you're Goddess Wushuang?

40
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,910
What are you talking about?

41
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,000
I mean,

42
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,680
sorry, Goddess Wushuang,

43
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:54,680
you've been…

44
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,440
exposed.

45
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:58,710
Don't talk nonsense.

46
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:00,680
Actually, it's not hard to guess.

47
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,400
If anyone

48
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:04,520
had paid close attention to you,

49
00:04:04,690 --> 00:04:06,180
they'd have noticed you're different.

50
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,630
Look,

51
00:04:07,970 --> 00:04:08,880
you're the Youhu Clan's

52
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:10,280
High Priest's handmaiden

53
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,470
and a friend to the War Demons.

54
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,800
You're kind to humans as well.

55
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,870
Besides, your craftsmanship is remarkable.

56
00:04:17,269 --> 00:04:19,310
The Youhu Clan, the War Demons, and the human race

57
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:21,870
have been at odds for over a century,

58
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,480
fighting and spilling blood.

59
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,160
Yet you've managed to deal with them all

60
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,270
and remain neutral.

61
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,630
Isn't that strange?

62
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,510
That's all you have

63
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:29,870
to determine my identity?

64
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,830
No, no, no.

65
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,310
I don't need all that.

66
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,240
The first time I saw you,

67
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:36,159
I knew who you were.

68
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,430
900 years ago…

69
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:42,310
you made a lamp.

70
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,600
Do you remember?

71
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,159
You're a weapon spirit?

72
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:52,000
Yes.

73
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,190
I've been around

74
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,270
for quite a while.

75
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,680
I thought in this lifetime,

76
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:01,800
I'd never have the chance

77
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,070
to see you again.

78
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,070
I didn't expect that lamp

79
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:07,310
to create a weapon spirit.

80
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,310
I thought it had been

81
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,270
destroyed in the war between gods and demons.

82
00:05:10,870 --> 00:05:11,680
Indeed.

83
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,160
This world

84
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:15,000
is full of unexpected things,

85
00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:16,560
and that's what makes it so fascinating.

86
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,240
Goddess Wushuang,

87
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,120
during those years when I was a lamp,

88
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,240
I kept watching you

89
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:22,830
and kept wondering

90
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,360
what kind of man

91
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,480
you'd fall for.

92
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,360
Would it be someone like Deity Taihe,

93
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,680
serious and dignified?

94
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,800
Or someone like Mr. Loong, humorous

95
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,630
and knowledgeable?

96
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,240
Thinking it over,

97
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,360
I figured it should be a combination of both.

98
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,159
In other words...

99
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,560
it should be someone like me.

100
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,159
But who would have thought

101
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,480
you'd fall for someone

102
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,560
like the High Priest of the Youhu Clan?

103
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,480
You came to kill him and take his hand, right?

104
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,000
Indulging yourself like this,

105
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,390
aren't you afraid

106
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,510
of being caught in a dilemma

107
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:00,070
and putting yourself in a difficult position?

108
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,360
It's not what you think.

109
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,630
You can't hide it.

110
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,000
The Divine Left Hand, created by you,

111
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,310
is now on him.

112
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,430
It's obvious why you're here.

113
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,680
I'm just worried about you,

114
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,920
and I feel sorry for him.

115
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:13,680
So tell me,

116
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,000
if one day

117
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:17,040
he learns who you are

118
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,070
and why you came,

119
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,560
how do you think he'll feel?

120
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,680
He won't find out.

121
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,510
Is this why

122
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,950
you called me here today?

123
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,720
No, no, no.

124
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,560
Goddess Wushuang,

125
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,070
I exist because of you,

126
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,390
so I owe you my life.

127
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,600
There's something

128
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,600
I've kept buried in my heart.

129
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:43,070
It's a secret of great importance.

130
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,360
If anything goes wrong,

131
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:46,600
it could lead to the collapse of heaven and earth

132
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,270
and the destruction of the Six Realms.

133
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,510
Now,

134
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,680
I want to tell you about it.

135
00:06:58,159 --> 00:07:00,830
During the war between gods and demons, I saw with my own eyes

136
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,040
that Deity Taihe was the Demon God.

137
00:07:07,850 --> 00:07:09,200
When I discovered this,

138
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,350
I fled to the mortal realm in a panic.

139
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:13,600
Since then,

140
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,510
I've never mentioned it to anyone.

141
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:19,630
I'd never lie to you.

142
00:07:23,430 --> 00:07:24,920
Thank you for telling me this.

143
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,390
Fu Jiuyun.

144
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,070
As a weapon spirit,

145
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:34,159
you're one in a million

146
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,870
and have lived among mortals for a long time.

147
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,720
In the mortal realm,

148
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,830
through ups and downs,

149
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:41,070
you've already carved your own path.

150
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,120
I can see that your sea of consciousness

151
00:07:43,430 --> 00:07:44,680
is shrouded in fog.

152
00:07:45,070 --> 00:07:46,720
You've forgotten the most important thing.

153
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:50,159
Your path is not in the Divine Realm,

154
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,750
nor is it with me.

155
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:55,040
Let me clear the fog for you

156
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,480
so you can see your way forward.

157
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,510
Go now.

158
00:08:11,150 --> 00:08:12,440
We'll meet again someday.

159
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,540
[Yandu City]

160
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,910
Why is the sky suddenly so bright?

161
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:03,600
Is it an omen of natural disasters?

162
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:05,620
Steamed buns!

163
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,200
Freshly steamed buns!

164
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,000
Thin skin, big filling, piping hot.

165
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:10,270
Sir, have some buns.

166
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:12,200
Mom, I want some buns.

167
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,940
Now you know it hurts!

168
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,910
It hurts.

169
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,480
Do you still know who I am?

170
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,410
You've been out for three days,

171
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,870
gambling day and night.

172
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:21,000
How much did you lose this time?

173
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,080
I won this time.

174
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:25,440
Amazing! Amazing!

175
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,550
All talk and no action is fake skill.

176
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,360
All action and no talk is dumb skill.

177
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,720
Talking and doing—that's real skill!

178
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:33,390
My father and I just arrived here.

179
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:34,670
We don't know anyone or anything about this place.

180
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:36,080
We need money to continue our travel.

181
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,480
If you can spare a little change, we'd be grateful.

182
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,270
Sir, we just got

183
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,000
some new calligraphy works and paintings.

184
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,840
Are you interested?

185
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:40,750
Would you like to take a look?

186
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,120
Would you like to buy calligraphy works or paintings?

187
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,390
No, I can't afford them.

188
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,790
Sir, sir.

189
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:48,320
Sir, please help me out.

190
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,270
I'm a poor little cripple.

191
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:50,240
Please show some pity

192
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,510
and give me a copper coin.

193
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,750
Sir, I haven't eaten for a long time.

194
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:55,270
Please help me out.

195
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:01,030
You have a death wish?

196
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,120
How dare you hit me!

197
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,870
Sir, this is the place.

198
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,370
Here you are.

199
00:10:28,070 --> 00:10:28,650
Have a seat.

200
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:33,200
I thought you wouldn't come.

201
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,960
You're buying me a meal.

202
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,030
How could I not come?

203
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,600
You like peace and quiet,

204
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,750
so I thought you might find this place too noisy.

205
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:41,840
Here, let's drink.

206
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:50,600
This wine

207
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:51,770
is a bit bland.

208
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,000
I don't like it either.

209
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,910
Then why did you order a whole jar of it?

210
00:10:58,670 --> 00:10:59,790
Parting ways with my friend,

211
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:01,380
I can't help but feel a little down.

212
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,260
You're a really good friend.

213
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,870
Though the wine's not so good,

214
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:07,550
it can still lessen the sorrow a bit.

215
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:08,910
You're leaving?

216
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:10,550
Back to Baitou Mountain.

217
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,000
Didn't you just leave that place?

218
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,480
I did.

219
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,150
Let me tell you,

220
00:11:15,290 --> 00:11:15,790
when I was alone

221
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:16,710
back in Baitou Mountain,

222
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,870
I felt so bored.

223
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:20,600
I heard Yandu City is bustling and prosperous,

224
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,670
so I came to take a look.

225
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,720
But after coming here,

226
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,440
I found it just so-so.

227
00:11:25,270 --> 00:11:26,360
Everyone's

228
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,670
obsessed with fame and fortune.

229
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,120
If this is the mortal world,

230
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:31,550
it's not worth staying for.

231
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,440
Sounds like

232
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,730
you've found your way to enlightenment.

233
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,330
Stop flattering me.

234
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,030
If we're talking about enlightenment,

235
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:43,270
you had the courage to cut off the Five Sins.

236
00:11:43,630 --> 00:11:45,330
I could never manage that.

237
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,080
Yuanzhong,

238
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,120
in a blink of an eye,

239
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:00,440
we've known each other

240
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,720
for 60 years, right?

241
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:04,440
Almost.

242
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,510
How time flies.

243
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:10,870
Do you remember

244
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:12,200
when we first met?

245
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,440
You smashed my cave dwelling,

246
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,480
and I went to you angrily

247
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,790
to demand an explanation.

248
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:17,910
At that time,

249
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:19,510
you had just defeated the War Demons

250
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,600
and were so powerful with the Divine Left Hand.

251
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:24,030
You were riding high on success.

252
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,200
Let me tell you,

253
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,270
before I met you,

254
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:27,910
I made

255
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:29,150
a lot of preparations.

256
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:30,600
I thought there'd be

257
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,270
a fierce battle between us for sure.

258
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:33,440
But unexpectedly,

259
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,270
when we met,

260
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:36,410
you just handed me a chest full of gold.

261
00:12:36,430 --> 00:12:38,240
It was a big chest of gold.

262
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,240
You have no idea.

263
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,600
I was completely dumbfounded.

264
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,020
I'd never seen that much gold in my life.

265
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:44,840
As a cultivator

266
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,360
who's about to ascend,

267
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:47,440
why do you still care so much

268
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,440
about money?

269
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,240
What's wrong with that?

270
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,960
Even immortals have to eat!

271
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:53,810
Someone like you,

272
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,910
who once lived in wealth and luxury,

273
00:12:54,980 --> 00:12:56,070
wouldn't understand.

274
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,750
Actually,

275
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,670
I was injured at that time.

276
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:04,600
I was worried I couldn't beat you,

277
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:07,270
so I resorted to that trick.

278
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,720
Is... is that so?

279
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,510
At that time, I just thought

280
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,630
the High Priest of the Youhu Clan

281
00:13:19,630 --> 00:13:20,890
looked pretty intimidating,

282
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:22,430
but he was actually reasonable—

283
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,480
someone worth befriending.

284
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,750
So?

285
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,750
So when you asked me later

286
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:28,030
to watch over Kai Shan,

287
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,200
I agreed.

288
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,550
When I was young,

289
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,150
