443
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,590
I talked about my dreams,

444
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:17,360
my life,

445
00:23:18,430 --> 00:23:19,360
and myself.

446
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:21,720
Later,

447
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:24,720
