448
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:27,840
doubt,

449
00:23:27,010 --> 00:23:29,150
♫Time never defeats the fleeting world♫

450
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:29,500
betrayal,

451
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:32,550
♫Stars turn, shining upon the passing traveler♫

452
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,350
the loss of my home,

453
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:33,510
