462
00:23:49,010 --> 00:23:55,570
♫I'm willing to risk my life for this♫

463
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:50,160
I wondered…

464
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:53,160
was I wrong?

465
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,440
