472
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:06,140
♫Fingertips tracing your outline♫

473
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,070
and there was no need for me to intervene

474
00:24:06,070 --> 00:24:07,960
with the power of the Divine Hand.

475
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:09,280
♫I wish to see through you♫

476
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,720
Maybe

477
00:24:10,550 --> 00:24:13,270
