I'll go stay at your house next time

855
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:36,920
and let you know

856
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:38,710
what it feels like to be struck by lightning.

857
00:42:39,590 --> 00:42:41,360
You're beating around the bush to avoid paying.

858
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:43,150
Immortals have to play fair too!

859
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:44,760
If you don't pay me today,

860
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:45,960
you're not going anywhere.

861
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,280
I wasn't planning

862
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:48,070
to go anywhere anyway.

863
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:49,110
Trying to provoke me, huh?

864
00:42:49,360 --> 00:42:50,740
I'll just stick with you all day.

865
00:42:54,230 --> 00:42:55,030
Do as you please.

866
00:42:55,030 --> 00:42:56,230
I've got no money.

867
00:42:56,260 --> 00:42:57,090
Take my life if you want it.

868
00:42:58,190 --> 00:42:58,960
I've never seen

869
00:42:58,960 --> 00:43:00,480
an immortal as shameless as you!

870
00:43:00,810 --> 00:43:01,890
Don't go!

871
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:03,590
I'm talking to you!

872
00:43:03,920 --> 00:43:05,320
Don't go! You hear me?

873
00:43:17,150 --> 00:43:18,120
Yuanzhong.
